Output docs/demo-form.gif

Set Width 88
Set Height 26
Set FontSize 13
Set Framerate 15
Set Padding 16
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set LoopOffset 0%

Env SAGETUI_DEMO_MODE "1"
Env SAGETUI_EXIT_AFTER_MS "11000"

Hide
Type "dotnet run --project samples/04-InteractiveForm/InteractiveForm.fsproj --no-build -c Release"
Enter
Sleep 2.5s
Show

Sleep 12s
